<h4>Hello <%= "#{@application.firstname} #{@application.lastname}" %>,</h4>
<p>
  This is a confirmation that you are enrolled for the Michigan
  Math & Science Scholars High School Program for the Summer <%= @camp_config.camp_year %> camp.
</p>
<p>
  Continue to check your email and the status area of the MMSS student portal for updates on your application.

    <div style="text-align: center; margin: 20px 0;">
      <%= link_to 'MMSS Student Portal', @url, style: "background-color: #1a5a96; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;" %>
  </div>
</p>
<p>
  Retain the login id: <strong><%= @user_detail.email %></strong>
  and password that you created during the application process. You
  will need it to refer back to the application web site to review the
  events associated with your application.
</p>
